@startuml
title PQR Hybrid Lakehouse - Contexto General (Local Docker)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
left to right direction

actor "Analista / Estudiante" as User
actor "Equipo de Datos" as DataTeam
cloud "Fuentes Operacionales\n(PQRS JSONL / APIs / CSV)" as Sources
cloud "Navegador Web" as Browser

rectangle "PQR Hybrid Lakehouse (Entorno Local)" as System {
  package "Control Plane" {
    [PostgreSQL + PostGIS\nSchemas: auth/meta/bronze/silver/gold] as PG
  }

  package "Data Plane" {
    [RustFS\nS3-compatible Object Storage] as S3
  }

  package "Compute Plane" {
    [Dask Scheduler] as DaskS
    [Dask Workers] as DaskW
  }

  package "Orquestacion" {
    [Prefect Server] as Prefect
  }

  package "Supabase Overlay" {
    [Kong API Gateway] as Kong
    [GoTrue Auth] as Auth
    [PostgREST] as Rest
    [Postgres Meta] as Meta
    [Supabase Studio] as Studio
  }

  package "Observabilidad" {
    [Prometheus] as Prom
    [Grafana] as Grafana
  }

  package "Serving y Analitica" {
    [Streamlit] as Streamlit
    [Metabase] as Metabase
  }
}

Sources --> S3 : Eventos raw
DataTeam --> Prefect : Ejecuta / programa flows
Prefect --> DaskS : Dispara jobs
DaskS --> DaskW : Distribuye tareas
DaskW --> S3 : Lee raw/escribe parquet
DaskW --> PG : Carga Bronze/Silver/Gold\n+ metadatos/calidad

Kong --> Auth : /auth
Kong --> Rest : /rest/v1
Studio --> Meta : introspeccion DB
Meta --> PG : catalogo SQL
Rest --> PG : lectura/escritura REST
Auth --> PG : usuarios/sesiones

Prom --> DaskS : scrape /metrics
Grafana --> Prom : dashboards

Streamlit --> PG : consultas KPIs
Metabase --> PG : BI SQL

User --> Browser
Browser --> Prefect : UI (4200)
Browser --> Studio : UI (3002)
Browser --> Grafana : UI (3001)
Browser --> Metabase : UI (3000)
Browser --> Streamlit : UI (8501)
Browser --> DaskS : Dashboard (8787)
Browser --> Kong : API REST (8000)

@enduml
